&lt;div style="width:1px;height:1px;overflow-x:hidden;overflow-y:hidden"&gt;Pretty near the core of American culture is the automobile. The average family owns two of&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style="width:1px;height:1px;overflow-x:hidden;overflow-y:hidden"&gt;three of them, and from high school on, all of us, men and women, see cars as the extension of&lt;/div&gt;
